Installation of the binary windows package (spams-2.3.win32-py2.7.exe)
This package is for python-2.7

Just download and execute spams-2.3.win32-py2.7.exe
All external DLLs need are included and will be installed in 
 C:\Python27\Lib\site-packages
But you need to install packages numpy and scipy for python-2.7 from http://www.numpy.org

To run the given examples, open a "command" window and type :
cd C:\Python27\test
..\python test_spams.py -h
..\python test_spams.py

